routes.description: 2 Line runs between South Bellevue Station and Downtown Redmond Station seven days a week
1 Line runs between Lynnwood City Center Station and Federal Way Downtown Station seven days a week

description.value:
Passengers will see out-of-service trains departing South Bellevue Station. These trains will continue to International District Station. Passengers will not be affected during these operator trainings.

Please pay attention to the train head signs or listen to the audio announcements before you board your train.

summary.value: Starting December 22, Sound Transit will be conducting operator trainings from South Bellevue Station to International District Station in preparation for the 2 Line extension opening.
